#lesson4
开发中可以提升效率的方法
1. webpack's Watch Mode
2. webpack-dev-server
3. source map debug
4. hot module replacement
  style + replace module + debug
  (ps:import and accept should has the same name: hmr.js is not equals to hmr)

#lesson5
开发中的插件利器
1. yar add postcss-loader --dev
   .postcssrc || postcss.config.js
   import vs css-loader importLoaders:num
2. yarn add less less-loader --dev
   import can auto process by less-loader
3. cssnano
4. babel-loader

